[cite_start][cite: 62] Technical Architecture
The project uses a simple client-server architecture:

| Component | Technology | RÃ´le |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| Backend | Python (Flask) | [cite_start]Data management, connection to the DX Cluster (Telnet), score calculation (AI Score), caching, and servicing JSON endpoints[cite: 62]. |
| Frontend | HTML/CSS/JS | [cite_start]User Interface[cite: 62]. [cite_start]Leaflet for mapping, Chart.js for charts, Vanilla JS for dynamic updates and interactions (QRA, filters)[cite: 63]. |
| Data Flow | JSON, Telnet | [cite_start]Flask retrieves spots from the Cluster and formats them into JSON[cite: 63]. [cite_start]JavaScript queries the Flask endpoints (/spots.json, /wanted.json, etc.) every 3 seconds to update the interface[cite: 64]. |

