Interface Usage Guide

Set Your QRA Locator In the COMMAND DECK control panel:

Enter your QRA Locator (e.g., JN33, JN33BB). Click on GO.

The system will center the map and update all distance calculations based on your location. It also displays "Valid / Valide" for 40 seconds.

Watchlist Management Enter a call sign (e.g., K1TTT) in the WATCHLIST field and click ADD. Spots for this call sign will be highlighted in yellow and trigger a voice alert (if VOICE: ON).


Alert Systems

Priority Target (SPD >= 70): Critical spots trigger an aggressive red flash and a thick border in the Live Stream and Top DX Wanted for immediate identification.

SURGE: A banner appears when a significant burst of activity is detected on a specific band.

OUVERTURE DETECTEE (OPENING DETECTED): The PROPAGATION HISTORY panel visually alerts if the Magic Bands (12m/10m/6m) are actively open.

